'''Sutta Chwituskak''' (literally "Flung Spears" in [[Sith (language)|Sith]]<ref name="Grossblatt e-mail">{{EmailCite|email=Wookieepedia:Email/Ben Grossblatt|creator=[[Ben Grossblatt]]|date=2012-07-16}}</ref>) was the proper name of the '''Bolt of Hatred''', an ancient [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] [[Force power/Legends|technique]] conjured through [[Sith sorcery/Legends|magic]]. The [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force-sensitive/Legends|user]] would create a radiant sphere of pure hatred which they could hurl at any target in their direct line of sight. Knowledge of the ability was recorded by the [[Sith Lord/Legends|Sith Lord]] [[Sorzus Syn]] in her journals.<ref name="TBoS">''[[Book of Sith: Secrets from the Dark Side]]''</ref>

